żFrom Phil to Alina, my wife and love of my life.
For memories of lunches and moments shared
in Berkeley Square Mayfair and in
the London Town that we grew to love together
and call our home."┴
żThe IATP - Raising Asbestos Awareness Together
Remembering those whose lives have been affected by asbestos
The living owe it to those who can no longer speak
to tell their story for them"╩
ăTo Our Beloved Robert Burness
02.07.1950 - 16.05.2010
That laughing eye, whose sunny beam
Our memory would not cherish less,
And oh, that smile! whose joyous gleam
No mortal language can express"╠
